text: The 2019 UAE Super Cup will be the 19th and the 12th Professional UAE Super Cup, an annual football match played between the winners of the previous season's Pro-League and President's Cup. It will be contested at Al Maktoum Stadium, between Sharjah and Shabab Al-Ahli Dubai, winners of 2018–19 Pro- League and 2018–19 President's Cup respectively. ==Details== {| width=92% |- | | |} {|
